---
interface Props {
  bg?: string;
}
const { bg = '' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class={bg}>
  <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-6 pt-8 pb-24 font-body text-bfc-brand-fg/80 text-xl space-y-8">
    <p>
      Bath Film Club is a monthly film discussion group based in Bath and organised through Discord.
      Each month we explore a new theme, discover new films, and share our thoughts in a relaxed and
      friendly discussion.
    </p>
    <p>
      The process is simple. A theme is chosen, members nominate films that fit the theme, and five
      films are selected to form a shortlist. Members then vote for their favourites, and the two
      most popular films become the focus of that month's discussion.
    </p>
    <p>
      Watch the films in your own time, then join us to share your perspective, hear different
      viewpoints, and discover something new.
    </p>
    <p>
      Not sure if it's for you? Take a look through our previous themes and film selections using
      the menu and, if it sounds like something you'd enjoy, join us on Discord and come along to
      the next discussion.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 pt-10 text-amber-400/80 text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">
      <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
